name: APA Corporation Common Stock
description: Based in Houston, APA Corp. is an independent exploration and production company. It operates primarily in the U.S., Egypt, the North Sea, and Suriname. At year-end 2021, proved reserves totaled 913 million barrels of oil equivalent, with net reported production of 388 mboe/d (64% of which was oil and natural gas liquids, with the remainder comprising natural gas).
